responses.body:
{
    "id": {{urlParam 'user_id'}},

    "firstName": "{{firstName}}",
    "lastName": "{{lastName}}",
    "isAdmin": {{oneOf (array true false)}},
    "isEnabled": {{oneOf (array true false)}},
    "activationStatus": "confirmed",
    "dateCreated": "{{dateTimeShift date=now format='yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss' days=(int -20 -10)}}",
    "lastUpdated": "{{dateTimeShift date=now format='yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss' days=(int -20 -10)}}",
    "version": 1,
    "bypassSsoEnforcement":false
}

responses.label: container asset

headers.value: Content-Type, Origin, Accept, Authorization, Content-Length, X-Requested-With
